            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d34855-Hd1e108">Rubrica 12</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d34855-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De satisffactione illate iniurie</head>
            <!--NOTE: the headings of rubric 12 and 13 appear to be mixed up, header of rubric 13 precedes heading of rubric 12 but the body paragraphs are in the correct order-->
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34855-d1e121">
               <!--this paragraph precedes header, header has been moved to follow after this paragraph-->
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34855-Rd1e124">ISidorus soliloquiorum libro 2. capitulo 
               <lb ed="#O"/>22.</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34855-Qd1e125">Si contristaueris in 
               <lb ed="#O"/>aliquo fratrem tuum <sic>satisfac</sic> illi. Si pec<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>caueris 
               in eum age penitentiam 
               <lb ed="#O"/>coram illo. ¶ Si offenderis 
               <lb ed="#O"/>cui quod repropitiare eum prece. Per<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>ge 
               uelociter ad reconciliationem 
               <lb ed="#O"/>proximi tui. ¶ Offensioni tue 
               <lb ed="#O"/>cito ueniam postula. ¶ Non re<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>quiescas 
               nisi reconciliatus fu<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>eris 
               fratri.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34855-d1e114">
               ¶ De satisfatione illa<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>te 
               iniurie. Rubrica. 12 <sic>a</sic>
            </p>
